01:52:57,253 --> 01:52:58,379
Bill.

2122
01:52:59,522 --> 01:53:00,955
You're welcome.
You're welcome.

2123
01:53:01,024 --> 01:53:02,457
Vin, I..

2124
01:53:02,525 --> 01:53:03,617
Bill, listen.

2125
01:53:03,693 --> 01:53:06,457
Take your time.
Pick the right words.

2126
01:53:06,529 --> 01:53:09,464
Get back to New York.
Give me a call.

2127
01:53:09,532 --> 01:53:10,624
Thank you.

2128
01:53:11,768 --> 01:53:13,235
OK.

2129
01:53:13,303 --> 01:53:15,464
Vinny, you did
a terrific job.

2130
01:53:15,538 --> 01:53:16,402
Thanks. Thanks.

2131
01:53:16,473 --> 01:53:17,906
You got an open invitation

2132
01:53:17,974 --> 01:53:20,408
anytime you want
to come down here.

2133
01:53:20,477 --> 01:53:22,911
We'll get us
a deer next time.

2134
01:53:22,979 --> 01:53:24,412
If I don't leave now,

2135
01:53:24,481 --> 01:53:27,416
I might never
be able to leave.

2136
01:53:27,484 --> 01:53:30,578
Mr. Gambini,
I have a fax here

2137
01:53:30,653 --> 01:53:32,917
from the clerk
of New York.

2138
01:53:34,491 --> 01:53:36,925
I owe you
an apology, sir.

2139
01:53:36,993 --> 01:53:39,427
I'm honored
to shake your hand.

2140
01:53:39,496 --> 01:53:41,930
"Win some, lose some."

2141
01:53:41,998 --> 01:53:43,260
Your courtroom manner

2142
01:53:43,333 --> 01:53:44,766
