2152
01:54:10,026 --> 01:54:13,723
I had a friend send
a fax to the judge

2153
01:54:13,797 --> 01:54:19,394
confirming the very impressive
legal stature of Jerry Callo.

2154
01:54:19,469 --> 01:54:22,905
What friends you got
in the Clerk's Office?

2155
01:54:22,972 --> 01:54:24,405
Your friend.

2156
01:54:24,474 --> 01:54:25,907
My friend?

2157
01:54:25,975 --> 01:54:27,465
Judge Malloy.

2158
01:54:29,612 --> 01:54:32,410
So what's your problem?

2159
01:54:32,482 --> 01:54:36,316
My problem is I wanted
to win my first case

2160
01:54:36,386 --> 01:54:38,149
without any help
from anybody.

2161
01:54:38,221 --> 01:54:40,655
Well, I guess
that plan's moot.

2162
01:54:40,723 --> 01:54:42,418
Yeah.

2163
01:54:42,492 --> 01:54:45,586
You know, this could be a sign
of things to come.

2164
01:54:45,662 --> 01:54:47,596
You win
all your cases,

2165
01:54:47,664 --> 01:54:49,598
but with somebody
else's help, right?

2166
01:54:49,666 --> 01:54:51,600
You win
case after case,

2167
01:54:51,668 --> 01:54:55,104
and then afterwards,
you have to go up to somebody,

2168
01:54:55,171 --> 01:54:57,605
and you have
to say thank you.

2169
01:54:57,674 --> 01:54:59,107
Oh, my God!

2170
01:54:59,175 --> 01:55:01,439
What a fucking nightmare!

2171
01:55:05,415 --> 01:55:07,440
I won my first case.

2172
01:55:07,517 --> 01:55:09,781
You know what this means.

2173
01:55:09,853 --> 01:55:11,616
You think I'll marry you.

2174
01:55:11,688 --> 01:55:14,452
What, you're not going
to marry me now?

2175
01:55:14,524 --> 01:55:17,550
No way. You can't win
a case by yourself.

2176
01:55:17,627 --> 01:55:18,958
You're fucking useless.

2177
01:55:21,464 --> 01:55:23,364
I thought we'd get
married this weekend.

2178
01:55:23,433 --> 01:55:25,663
You don't get it,
do you?

2179
01:55:25,735 --> 01:55:26,895
That is not romantic.

2180
01:55:26,970 --> 01:55:29,131
I want a wedding
in church

2181
01:55:29,205 --> 01:55:30,900
with bridesmaids
and flowers.

2182
01:55:30,974 --> 01:55:31,307
Oh, how many times

2183
01:55:31,308 --> 01:55:32,399
Oh, how many times

2184
01:55:32,475 --> 01:55:35,410
did you say that spontaneous
is romantic?

2185
01:55:35,478 --> 01:55:37,412
Hey, a burp is spontaneous.

2186
01:55:37,480 --> 01:55:39,414
A burp is not romantic.

